https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMTVfMTMz/MDAxNzM5NTg3ODk5NDYw.M6bMo6CMJQ9PfOvObSc6RkoPZ3BJFzU06tILXgOrZ-Ug.3KXwkYGH87Jvr4FsS2w0x7Zc5AIOJ9nUa9LBoNJOZmwg.PNG/%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%801.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-84d25f91-54df-4358-9689-3d524b907443\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50edb1b9-8de7-4925-b529-1769e4beb6be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3be973bf-bf73-4947-ae35-bea2ba707759\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단상자는 가장 일반적인 종이가 아이보리나 마닐라, CCP 계열입니다. 이 패키지 종이는 내구성이 탁월하면서도 단가적으로도 메리트를 가지고 있는 것이 분명합니다. 하지만 특별한 제품이 들어가는 경우 특수한 종이로 돋보이게 제작할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b3a8e54d-8a9c-4960-9a69-2a21b367ec9d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-652f795f-9610-4262-9484-312973e93067\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-218c796b-40a2-4dc7-8422-e31b4966326e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-23b3185e-94fd-47d2-a4e2-9775e6e4093b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>패키지에서 일반적으로 사용되는 종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d0429-8245-433b-884d-e22587d8ee53\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-992a0710-e4b2-47b6-bb2f-239dd0317399\" style=\"color:#555555;\">마닐라용지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88294d72-3bd2-4a3a-921b-c7f4824a21ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2677f37d-e230-406e-8924-3fc8e4c83be4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">BV / BW 용 편면 코팅지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8014a69a-1826-4140-985a-2d092d946c77\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-37a8187e-7d5c-4e03-a800-8a7136b09a61\" style=\"color:#555555;\">CCP지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d70f3b0b-0bcb-4ac9-85c2-72d0f44adf42\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d09d5baa-20b8-4978-916a-3f298728a34a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아이보리 류</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb8524bb-2fa0-4298-ac08-63abae0153f6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cc7bf98a-9891-457b-9ad2-ac302dd60d41\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로얄 아이보리류</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-363cce85-81c3-4d27-91bb-147b5595debe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-76460864-d661-4a03-8d86-392a95d0bd6a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-645132e6-4411-4bd2-ba5c-4b78f9e77b41\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fa6f5465-cdaf-4856-b59e-9e86c9f33e5c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 일반적인 박스용지 말고 특별한 종이를 사용하고 싶다면 흑지나 색지를 사용하는 것입니다. 보통 아이보리에 검정 인쇄를 하면 똑같은 효과를 기대할 수도 있으나 여러 가지 측면에서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ba45a74-1bcc-47bb-955b-14c2fb75d465\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\"><b>흑지, 색지보다 못한 결과물</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-28d605cf-7f1a-442c-bb96-4d90f70e2376\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 받아 보실 수 있습니다. 그렇기 때문에 단가적인 고려가 충분하다면 흑지, 또는 색지를 사용하여 제작하는 것을 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d45cd076-7181-4272-a2ef-f91db9e75cde\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fc12a37d-2d52-4173-84c8-df6a16d971dd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-afd96a68-dfd9-4aab-ad8a-f718330c1b6d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-876a37d3-fc2d-4075-baaa-813315770c01\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>다음은 실제 인쇄시 발생된 사례롤 설명드리고자 합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c46ac024-7ea6-41ef-bff3-e9a08dec1330\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9c085ee5-f066-46bd-b2e5-150804da461f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">--------------------------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5af27d22-467b-45aa-a3d9-f0c3e8a40773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-adcac6ad-162a-48c4-b293-3685dc74820b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>A  Type : 아이보리에 흑색 인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2553b93a-b1bf-4494-ae53-7580d0dc8cc6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3e063c10-1827-4e12-b2aa-787046a4fef0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">--------------------------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f8c56a7c-bf44-4f86-8f74-1033c321ef5d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-17adea84-4a75-4996-a59e-78288509d415\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c75b5a41-b61c-4763-b983-260126cc244e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-76346e9a-f83b-47a5-922f-c83f44c36fb3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· 종이 : 아이보리 350g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91a18ae9-3b2d-4d92-bbd5-5a516bd2a459\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2b58cb5e-50b4-4928-8a1d-e1c95cb57c2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· 인쇄 : 검정 인쇄 백 누끼 작업으로 디자인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35787b19-da5b-474f-bc2e-755fc08a4b15\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-61710835-67df-41d4-a7e0-12a1bcab759a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">· 코팅 : 단면 무광코팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e32b241f-419f-4ca4-9716-542fc05eec5f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-635af314-8e13-47bd-b19d-c26dfc853cda\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1c43605-4f1b-45c4-af3b-122963a2e33e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-435feecf-d06d-4444-b0ee-2c22060abb96\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>* 문제점</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-420b0378-cf55-4694-a31f-404b824c4312\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-420b0378-cf55-4694-a31f-404b824c4312\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMTVfMjUy/MDAxNzM5NTg4NTgxMDA4.jk56b3XLGYnLPIsH3D52zhFOepEawI-7r3CPh4vujYsg.EAYm_gMLqHrFpES0Ce8UfG00TyeXKiEVPUDw9dzH11wg.PNG/%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%801.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1438\", \"originalHeight\" : \"661\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMTVfMjUy/MDAxNzM5NTg4NTgxMDA4.jk56b3XLGYnLPIsH3D52zhFOepEawI-7r3CPh4vujYsg.EAYm_gMLqHrFpES0Ce8UfG00TyeXKiEVPUDw9dzH11wg.PNG/%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%801.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9cf02bdf-b64b-4236-bc42-f2ffcb14241c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-903b9e8a-49a4-40f7-8aeb-c52927eaca18\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8a78bf70-93bb-4a79-a878-7169a76cad9b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정확하게는 사고라고 볼 수 없지만 이렇게 제작을 하게 되면 조립 후 하얀 종이 부분이 노출되어 보기 싫어지게 나옵니다. 이런 현상을 인쇄용어에서는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e1cc0180-9f7d-4c78-b686-8447c5e67aac\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>히로</b></span><span class=\"se-f